Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.selenium.content.management

Annotation Interface SwitchToFrame

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({METHOD,TYPE}) @Repeatable(Frames.class) public @interface SwitchToFrame
Defines a frame to switch to. Sequence of SwitchToFrame annotations defines a frame path to target content
